[Name]  ntfsprogs
[Summary]  NTFS Utilities
[Description]  This package contains several utilities for the Windows NTFS filesystem. mkntfs	   - to create an NTFS filesystem ntfslabel	 - to change a label ntfsresize  - to resize an NTFS filesystem ntfsundelete - to recover a removed file from an NTFS filesystem PLEASE NOTE THAT THESE TOOLS ARE NOT YET STABLE AND CAN LEAD TO DATA LOSS !
[Suse Category]  System/Filesystems
[License]  GPL
[Homepage]  http://linux-ntfs.sf.net/
